this is how files are sent via ssh:

scp -ri keys/europe.pem production ec2-user@ec2-3-64-12-59.eu-central-1.compute.amazonaws.com:/home/ec2-user

to initialize libraries on instance:

curl -O https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py

python3 get-pip.py --user

Use ls -a ~ to find file

Add line to .bash_profile: export PATH=~/.local/bin:$PATH

source ~/.bash_profile

verify pip installation: pip --version

install the pip packages:

pip install pandas
pip install pandas_ta
pip install keras
pip install tensorflow-cpu
pip install python-binance
pip install binance-futures-connector
sudo yum install tmux (asks confirmation)

run python script:
tmux new -s script
python3 trader.py

Now you can disconnect from server. When you want to check the results type:
tmux a -t script 



